### 邮箱发送验证码
POST http://localhost:8000/user/email/send-code
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "purpose": "register"
}

### 邮箱注册并获取 JWT
POST http://localhost:8000/user/email/sign-up
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!",
  "nickname": "tester",
  "code": "1234"
}

### 邮箱验证码登录
POST http://localhost:8000/user/email/sign-in
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "code": "1234"
}

### 邮箱验证码重置密码
POST http://localhost:8000/user/email/reset-password
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "code": "1234",
  "newPassword": "NewPassw0rd!"
}

### 密码登录（passport 可用邮箱）
POST http://localhost:8000/user/sign-in
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "passport": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Passw0rd!"
}

### 获取个人资料（需要 Bearer Token）
GET http://localhost:8000/user/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 物品列表
GET http://localhost:8000/items

### 创建物品
POST http://localhost:8000/items
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Pen",
  "price": 9.9,
  "stock": 100,
  "description": "Blue pen"
}

### 获取物品详情
GET http://localhost:8000/items/1

### 更新物品
PUT http://localhost:8000/items/1
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

{
  "name": "Pen Pro",
  "price": 12.5,
  "stock": 90,
  "description": "Updated"
}

### 删除物品
DELETE http://localhost:8000/items/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
